  "markdown": "[![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68227ab77271320729baa06e/6841ca9b93320b34f1b6f17d_Black%20Wordmark.svg)](https://www.quantfi.us/)\n[Case Studies](https://www.quantfi.us/tools-case-studies)[About Us](https://www.quantfi.us/about)[Contact](https://www.quantfi.us/contact)\n[](https://www.linkedin.com/company/quantfi-us/)[Book a Call](https://www.quantfi.us/contact)\nLegal\n# Cookie Policy\n**Effective Date:** June 5, 2025\nUnder the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA), California residents have specific rights regarding their personal information.\nWe collect and use personal information, including identifiers (such as name, email, and IP address), browsing activity, purchase history, and geolocation data, to improve our services, provide customer support, and fulfill transactions. We do not sell personal data, but you have the right to opt out of any future sale should our practices change.\nCalifornia residents have the right to:\n  * Know what personal information we collect, how we use it, and whether we share it.\n  * Request deletion of personal information, subject to certain legal exceptions.\n  * Opt out of the sale of personal data (though we do not sell personal data).\n  * Not be subject to discrimination for exercising their rights.\n  * Avoid automated decision-making that significantly affects them.\n\n\nTo exercise these rights, you may contact us at cs@quantfi.us. You may also designate an authorized agent to submit requests on your behalf by providing written permission and verifying your identity.\nBefore processing any requests, we may require additional information to verify your identity. We will respond to verified requests within the timeframe required by law, typically within 45 days. If we deny a request, you have the right to appeal the decision by contacting us at the provided email.\nThis policy is drafted in English and shall govern any interpretations or disputes.\nFollow on Linkedin\nStay connected for regular tips, resources, and practical advice.\n[Follow QuantFi](https://www.linkedin.com/company/quantfi-us/)\n## Work With QuantFi\nConnect with us to discuss your goals and explore how our tailored financial support can help.\n[Schedule a Consultation](https://www.quantfi.us/contact)\n![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68227ab77271320729baa06e/68239bb22647b405c2f34fdb_CTA%20Grid.svg)\n![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68227ab77271320729baa06e/6822afddbf50ec64af9de4cf_Grid%20Background.png)![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68227ab77271320729baa06e/6822afddbf50ec64af9de4cf_Grid%20Background.png)\n[![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68227ab77271320729baa06e/6841ca9b93320b34f1b6f17d_Black%20Wordmark.svg)](https://www.quantfi.us/)[](https://www.linkedin.com/company/quantfi-us/)\n\u00a9 2026 QuantFi. All rights reserved.\nAll company names, logos and trademarks shown on this site are the property of their respective owners. Their display is for illustrative purposes only and does not imply any endorsement, sponsorship, affiliation or partnership with QuantFi. QuantFi makes no representations or warranties regarding any third-party products or services.\nCompany\n[About Us](https://www.quantfi.us/about)[Case Studies](https://www.quantfi.us/tools-case-studies)[Contact](https://www.quantfi.us/contact)[Present](https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1hdNZ5g4DW8zwM2vT6VJQmFm_fdE3p-gr?usp=sharing)\nLegal\n[Privacy Policy](https://www.quantfi.us/legal/privacy-policy)[Terms of Service](https://www.quantfi.us/legal/terms-of-service)[Refund & Return Policy](https://www.quantfi.us/legal/refund-and-return-policy)[Cookie Policy](https://www.quantfi.us/legal/cookie-policy)[Affiliate Disclosure](https://www.quantfi.us/legal/affiliate-disclosure)[California Disclosures](https://www.quantfi.us/legal/california-disclosures)\n",
