n\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-controls=\"w-nav-overlay-0\" aria-haspopup=\"menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><div class=\"menu-icon1\"><div class=\"menu-icon1_line-top\"></div><div class=\"menu-icon1_line-middle\"><div class=\"menu-icon1_line-middle-inner\"></div></div><div class=\"menu-icon1_line-bottom\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-nav-overlay\" data-wf-ignore=\"\" id=\"w-nav-overlay-0\"></div></div></div><section data-wf--image-hero--variant=\"base\" class=\"section_image_hero\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-hero is-smaller position-relative\"><div data-wf--heading-with-gradient--variant=\"base\" class=\"max-width-large-copy\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xsmall\"><div class=\"text-style-tagline\">Legal</div></div><div data-prevent-flicker=\"true\" data-word-reveal=\"true\" class=\"rich-text-heading w-richtext\"><h1>Cookie Policy</h1></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"gradient-blurb is-hero\"></div></section><section class=\"section_content31\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"content31_component\"><div class=\"content31_content\"><div class=\"text-rich-text w-richtext\"><p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> June 5, 2025</p><p>Under the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA), California residents have specific rights regarding their personal information.</p><p>We collect and use personal information, including identifiers (such as name, email, and IP address), browsing activity, purchase history, and geolocation data, to improve our services, provide customer support, and fulfill transactions. We do not sell personal data, but you have the right to opt out of any future sale should our practices change.</p><p>California residents have the right to:</p><ul role=\"list\"><li>Know what personal information we collect, how we use it, and whether we share it.</li><li>Request deletion of personal information, subject to certain legal exceptions.</li><li>Opt out of the sale of personal data (though we do not sell personal data).</li><li>Not be subject to discrimination for exercising their rights.</li><li>Avoid automated decision-making that significantly affects them.</li></ul><p>To exercise these rights, you may contact us at <a href=\"mailto:cs@quantfi.us\" target=\"_blank\">cs@quantfi.us</a>. You may also designate an authorized agent to submit requests on your behalf by providing written permission and verifying your identity.</p><p>Before processing any requests, we may require additional information to verify your identity. We will respond to verified requests within the timeframe required by law, typically within 45 days. If we deny a request, you have the right to appeal the decision by contacting us at the provided email.</p><p>This policy is drafted in English and shall govern any interpretations or disputes.</p></div></div><div class=\"content31_newsletter\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xsmall\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6-2\">Follow on Linkedin</div></div><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><p>Stay connected for regular tips, resources, and practical advice.</p></div><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/quantfi-us/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button w-button\">Follow QuantFi</a></div><div class=\"gradient-blurb is5\"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section data-wf--large-card-section--variant=\"base\" class=\"section_large-card\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div data-animate=\"fade-up\" class=\"layout1_component\" style=\"translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; opacity: 0; transform: translate(0px, 50px);\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid large-card\"><div class=\"large-card_content\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><h2 class=\"heading-style-h2\">Work With QuantFi</h2></div><p class=\"text-size-medium\">Connect with us to discuss your goals and explore how our tail